OL,3,CParts of ancient woodland destroyed by
OL,4,Cvandals
OL,6,FParts of an ancient woodland in
OL,7,FMaidstone have been destroyed by
OL,8,Fvandals.
OL,10,FMaidstone Borough Council said it is
OL,11,Finvestigating a number of incidents at
OL,12,FUpper Fullingpits Wood.
OL,14,FThey include chainsaws being used to
OL,15,Fchop down trees and vehicles driving
OL,16,Fover and dismantling sensitive areas
OL,17,Fof dead wood.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
