OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782147993
OL,3,CParts of ancient woodland destroyed by
OL,4,Cvandals
OL,6,FStag beetles - which are a protected
OL,7,Fspecies - live in the woodland, which
OL,8,Fis also a habitat for a rare type of
OL,9,Ffungus.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe authority said the destruction of
OL,17,Fdead and decaying wood was
OL,18,Fparticularly harmful as stag beetles
OL,19,Frely on this for part of their
OL,20,Flifecycle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
