OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782147993
OL,3,CParts of ancient woodland destroyed by
OL,4,Cvandals
OL,6,FIt said it will report incidents to
OL,7,Fthe police, where appropriate, and
OL,8,Finstall new signs to remind the public
OL,9,Fabout the importance of respecting the
OL,10,Fwoodland.
OL,12,FDeputy Leader of Maidstone Borough
OL,13,FCouncil Clive English said that while
OL,14,Fdeadwood "may not look important" it
OL,15,F"plays an important role in supporting
OL,16,Fwildlife".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
