FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782147993
OL,3,CParts of ancient woodland destroyed by
OL,4,Cvandals
OL,6,F"We are seeing an increase in
OL,7,Funauthorised cutting and removal of
OL,8,Fwood from council land, which in some
OL,9,Fcases is causing harm to protected
OL,10,Fareas," he added.
OL,12,F"We would ask residents to respect
OL,13,Fthese spaces and leave any natural
OL,14,Fmaterials where they are."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
